    "m_ObjectId": "4beebf9fdecc414583b74229e0ab5d76",
    "m_Title": "Channel IDs",
    "m_Content": "This shader is capable of handling 3 different UVs set of hexagonal grid tiles by splitting the RGB channels into 3 independent masks.\n\nThis enables up to 3 sets of individual random transformations, for example.\nEach of these transformation could be influenced differently thanks to these grids.",
